Title: ANN [ROC] RasputinOnline: The FIRST ICO for Adult Entertainment
Body: We have announced the trial of their Virtual Girlfriend concept to add to our current lineup of live streaming entertainment. The idea was first floated by one of their token holders which was suggested and discussed among the community on our Slack Channel and a as result the team have decided to put this idea into a beta trial.  The virtual girlfriend service will give the user an opportunity to have exclusive 24-hour connective access with one of the projects models of their choice for as long or as little as they like and will include the model wearing a personal camera everywhere she goes streaming live directly to her Virtual Boyfriend.  The projects long term plan to incorporate Virtual Reality build Virtual Reality will also be implemented with the Virtual Girlfriend product to make the service more immersive and interactive for the user.  RasputinOnline is a premium live broadcast Entertainment hub giving viewers from across the globe the medium to connect with in-house models on different levels. This fresh concept in entertainment for adults is centred around their custom-built broadcast studio which is set out as a party house, in this party house will live 60 models all coming from different parts of the world. Throughout the house there will be up to 100 cameras streaming life inside live, in High Definition, 24 hours per day. Cameras will be placed in all living areas, party and bar areas, swimming pool, gym and spa areas, the outdoor kitchen and hot tub area and in the bedrooms and bathrooms all of which broadcast live pictures and audio to our paying customers. Within the house they will also have up to 30 Live Show rooms. These live show rooms are private rooms where the models perform on camera broadcast to a live audience. Viewers can chat in an open chat room and tip the model at any time or they can engage in a private show with the model. It is the profit derived from these Live Show rooms that will be distributed quarterly to ROC token holders.  Members can vote on what type of weekly party will take place in the house, they can choose for their favourite model to take yoga classes, painting or piano lessons, they can buy roses, perfume and other gifts or they can send their favourite model a bottle of wine and a box of chocolates allowing our members to interact with our models in many different ways. This is a big step forward in the entertainment world and a first for a digital token issuing company  We have surpassed the $2 million mark and are about to hit the level required to activate Phase 2 of our project. We have a great community in our Slack channel and as a user driven project we are taking note of all suggestions and discussions and the ones that fit best will be implemented into our project or put to the investors to vote  We are a first in the digital token world and unique in the Entertainment world and the announcement of our Virtual Girlfriend concept is the first implementation of an investors suggestion.  https://ico.rasputinonline.com  Join our Slack Channel  https://rasputinonline.slack.com/join/shared_invite/MjE3NDQ4MzEyMTQ1LTE1MDEwODI3NjgtOTExZjYzODlhNw  If you have missed any of the events in our live broadcast studio, you can see pictures and updates on our Slack and also our Facebook page  https://www.facebook.com/rasputinonline

Author: ROC ICO
Title: ANN [ROC] RasputinOnline: The FIRST ICO for Adult Entertainment
Body: Hi. Thanks for your feedback, one thing I'd like to point out is the main feature of the ROC token is that holders of this token are entitled to receive shared profits paid as an ETH dividend every quarter.  The size of the dividend paid is what will increase the value of this token over time which will hopefully give long term token holders good protection from a pump and dump scenario. The company is also keeping 28% of all tokens as the company only makes its profit from the same dividends paid out to all token holders.  So even though there are 5,000,000 tokens being created, the maximum amount ever possible to reach the market will be 3.6 million tokens with 500k of those tokens (the development teams allocation) being locked for 12 months and the companies tokens being locked permanently.  Another notable feature is that the company and the development teams token allocation is only emitted proportionally to the amount of tokens sold to the public.   Our tokens are also redeemable for services and discounts within our project once it is live, for example 1 ROC token will be exchangeable for 3 months of website membership which will cost the fiat paying customer $89.95. ROC token holders will also be able to sell their tokens on our website to fiat customers who want to save money on the fiat prices.  https://ico.rasputinonline.com  Join our Slack Channel  https://rasputinonline.slack.com/join/shared_invite/MjE3NDQ4MzEyMTQ1LTE1MDEwODI3NjgtOTExZjYzODlhNw  If you have missed any of the events in our live broadcast studio, you can see pictures and updates on our Slack and also our Facebook page  https://www.facebook.com/rasputinonline  OP  https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=2002224.0
